{"tid":340342,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"明鏡網：習拍板調查海航","createTime":"2017-07-29T23:02:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-30T03:07:14.000Z","uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f04e4667b3ff951e8fdb4370e4f7472f06bece83","tid":340342,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T23:02:18.000Z","msg":"買咗廚叉/快運嘅人，坐穩機喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20170730/20106148\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20170730%2F20106148&d=S8PwmGUixMtWi6VUmInpDo9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=e0e62e00\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20170730%2F20106148&h=97a76a3b\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20170730/20106148</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>明鏡網：習拍板調查海航<br />\n俞正聲提議　國務院負責　繞過中紀委王岐山</strong><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】被指背後為中紀委書記王岐山家族撐腰的海南航空集團（簡稱海航），在海內外輿論和西方監管機構壓力下，傳被內地當局調查。海外消息指，中共高層決定對海航展開調查，包括海航近年大舉對外併購的資金及官商勾結等。但有學者認為，調查海航或是國家主席習近平拉攏民心及強權的權宜之計，是否真對利益集團後台動手，尚待觀察。<br />\n<br />\n美國中文媒體明鏡網昨在《點點今天事》透露，因流亡美國的中國富豪郭文貴爆料引起海內外關注的海航，經中南海高層拍板，已被列入當局打擊官商勾結及利益集團貪腐、預防金融危機的「金融反腐」調查名單，與早前被調查的安邦保險、明天系、大連萬達、上海復星等同在榜上。海航董事局主席陳峰、董事長王健等高層，將面臨當局調查。<br />\n<br />\n美監管部門指架構不清<br />\n<br />\n報道稱，對海航的調查由國務院負責，擔綱者是中共政治局委員、副總理馬凱，這意味着對海航的調查繞過了中紀委。中紀委書記是王岐山，而根據郭文貴爆料，海航問題源頭在王；王岐山不但是海航過去10來年財產爆炸式增長的原因，而且王家人還被指借海航斂財，包括被指是王私生子的貫君（Guan Jun），一度持有海航29%股權，是海航最大單一股東。<br />\n<br />\n報道還披露，中南海決定對金融領域開刀，是全國政協主席俞正聲提議，並獲習近平支持，政治局常委表決通過；這意味中國「金融沙皇」王岐山也同意；目前不清楚王是否會受波及。報道指，中共決定調查海航，或與海內外壓力有關。在內，海航近年高達400億美元（約3,108億港元）的瘋狂對外併購，與上述企業一樣屢被舉報涉資本外逃，對金融秩序造成危害；在外，海航成西方輿論焦點，《華爾街日報》、《紐約時報》、《金融時報》、彭博社等紛紛質疑海航並起底，美國金融監管部門也以「架構不清」為由介入。神秘大股東「貫君」將名下高達數百億美元的股權捐給成立不久的私人慈善基金，被美國檢方函令「20日內說清楚」；歐洲央行啟動對德意志銀行大股東海航等的調查。這一切令海航聲名狼藉。<br />\n<br />\n美國之音分析認為，中共對海航及安邦、萬達等公司調查，技術上主要源於金融危機，這些企業海外擴張的金錢主要來自與他們有利益關係的國有銀行，巨額外匯流出，對中國金融造成的危機非同小可；而且這些資金被投放到海外後，是否能重新返回中國成疑；為遏制資本外流，中共要出手進行整肅。<br />\n<br />\n專家：為穩金融　籠絡人心<br />\n<br />\n中國問題專家林和立對《蘋果》表示，中共自毛澤東開始，經濟領域反貪腐從來都與權力鬥爭相關。習近平拿海航及安邦等公司開刀「反貪」，一是整治已經危及到中國社會穩定的金融危機，二是要籠絡人心，因為這些企業與官場及高官家族已形成利益關係，官商勾結，大肆斂財，習要殺雞儆猴，但習是否會真的大開殺戒，逢貪必查，凡貪官必拿下，目前言之尚早。"},{"pid":"383a45bd4a31b56bd51d303420efd49111fe15b6","tid":340342,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T23:28:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ddb18428437db7dfaba0d32f2afec83e1e2aef5","tid":340342,"uid":101328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T23:30:41.000Z","msg":"講到航海響香港咁大影響 真係好想知道如果打得成香港會點？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a99c5cfac51122aa628175caf741cc52d7d28148","tid":340342,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T23:31:13.000Z","msg":"點解雞殺極都不盡？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70402032bc982f3df60788efeb8b075cc0b8390c","tid":340342,"uid":42921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T23:32:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講到航海響香港咁大影響 真係好想知道如果打得成香港會點？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n淨係買左幾塊地已經值得關注，如果撻訂會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51e03350c4176d2d6a2d29135f02c461ccf28703","tid":340342,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T23:40:28.000Z","msg":"查背後實際持有人<br />\n同埋邊個放水叫銀行做貸款<br />\n咁貸法等如走資人民幣<br />\n<br />\n香港啟德幾塊地已經完成收購<br />\n受影響係建築及發展項目資金<br />\n最壞情況只係fire sale 唔會撻訂"},{"pid":"34643dfb9224551dd40d3ccbd44488230fd73210","tid":340342,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T23:43:12.000Z","msg":"睇左下ANA飛日本機票，個時間真係"},{"pid":"104974362e5fc79af098137b5b4e98fe63420c03","tid":340342,"uid":103531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T23:47:06.000Z","msg":"王歧山咁耐都冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n明報想做第二個成報？"},{"pid":"d0a7b569b35e30601428bbf35dd395f40a5bdcdd","tid":340342,"uid":101328,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T23:49:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>王歧山咁耐都冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n明報想做第二個成報？</blockquote><br />\n明鏡阿，老友。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a65a323a91c2beeeb15f0d22e65ab6ad5dbb96ab","tid":340342,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T23:50:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>王歧山咁耐都冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n明報想做第二個成報？</blockquote><br />\n明鏡阿，老友。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"518041b97bd43580b68c5c1fe00fd5c2ff8ad198","tid":340342,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T23:53:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>王歧山咁耐都冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n明報想做第二個成報？</blockquote><br />\n明鏡阿，老友。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3267365fe3738a1a2f349e8a74828653a0d15dbd","tid":340342,"uid":58862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T23:55:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>王歧山咁耐都冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n明報想做第二個成報？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n習之後佢既權就係第二大<br />\n雖然話有分排名習李張王<br />\n<br />\n但大陸軍權警權真係要有口力人事先拎得"},{"pid":"063e75f48d54cf3f63ecbaf1ee910f4787a21e54","tid":340342,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T00:48:01.000Z","msg":"係時候清算了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7cedb90f832342e6997e475ef7b8fc50c0bcfe1","tid":340342,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T00:56:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>王歧山咁耐都冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n明報想做第二個成報？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n習之後佢既權就係第二大<br />\n雖然話有分排名習李張王<br />\n<br />\n但大陸軍權警權真係要有口力人事先拎得</blockquote><br />\n如果真係查王奇山，佢咁大仇口，大把人幫手做野，佢走定佬都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db49850db1a095497852023c55d0d29cba8305a1","tid":340342,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T01:03:30.000Z","msg":"係咪已經無記者貼身姓栗+蔡wah波單野"},{"pid":"76dba1bbe2e845852c38e43c53fd0ee3d342befa","tid":340342,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T01:06:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>王歧山咁耐都冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n明報想做第二個成報？</blockquote><br />\n明鏡阿，老友。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b304da378990940e242720e2f22e8b363914d8a","tid":340342,"uid":106247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T02:15:11.000Z","msg":"星期一long put海航<br />\n今次fat fat了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4e78c1632ff9d8468f7b0aa857aed47b2282c98","tid":340342,"uid":5715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T02:35:09.000Z","msg":"係真唔係啊，一陣又吹到大一大之後習種高度讚揚王生咪搞笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4feb0b420d1c4aef80163783f72eab97095c7864","tid":340342,"uid":6192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T03:07:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係真唔係啊，一陣又吹到大一大之後習種高度讚揚王生咪搞笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n689夠高度讚揚喇<br />\n最後咪又人比人趕落機"}]}